<div class="title">AMT in the Great White North</div>
<div class="substance">AMT & Cannabis</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=MackDaddy&Exact=1">MackDaddy</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; MackDaddy. "AMT in the Great White North: An Experience with AMT & Cannabis (exp8132)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 16, 2001. erowid.org/exp/8132</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
